&lt;p&gt;I wanted the label of the selected item to appear below the white background area, and when I select another Bottom Navigation Bar item, the label should stay there. So, the only way was to customize this package. That&amp;rsquo;s when we move to step 2 of this article.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="custom-curved-navigation-bar"&gt;Custom Curved Navigation Bar
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;I decided to create a new, more flexible package that can support both types: items with labels and items without labels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tadaa&amp;hellip; Here is my package: &lt;a class="link" href="https://pub.dev/packages/curved_labeled_navigation_bar" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;curved_labeled_navigation_bar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
